HEADWORD: Bluebill
<hw>Blue"bill`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>A duck of the genus <gen>Fuligula</gen>. Two American species
(<spn>Fuligula marila</spn> and <spn>Fuligula affinis</spn>) are common.
See <er>Scaup duck</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bluebird</ent>⟦br⟧
